headline: Iron Mountain Announces the Election of Christie Kelly to the Board of Directors
summary: PORTSMOUTH, N.H., October 21, 2025--Iron Mountain (NYSE: IRM), a global leader in information management services, today announced the election of Christie Kelly to the Board of Directors, effective October 21, 2025.
